/target

# Guest program and FRI VK are downloaded at build time by `build.rs` from the
# matching `zksync_airbender_verifier` release — never committed. The repo-wide
# .gitignore already excludes `dist`; we additionally exclude the downloaded
# FRI VK and the per-file `.tag` cache markers `build.rs` writes. `snark_vk.json`
# stays committed (it is not published as a release asset).
/vks/fri_vk.bin
/vks/*.tag
/guest/dist/app/*.tag
